hopobject.body: A financial advisor proextender online shopping "The Chrysler IPO is a textbook example of the difficultiesthat can occur when debt is converted into an ownership stake,as it was during Chrysler's bankruptcy, especially when that ownership stake is held by an interested party, in this case theUnited Auto Workers' healthcare trust," said Jack Nerad,executive editorial director and market analyst of auto researchfirm Kelley Blue Book.
